All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
BicycleJourney
A Bicycle Journey class that is used when Bicycle Journeys are added to
the Bicycle Journey database and getting Bicycle Journey related data.
BicycleJourneyController
A Controller class used to make accessing City Bicycle Journey related
data possible with the help of endpoints and other methods.
BicycleJourneyNotFoundException
This class is for Exceptions where a Bicycle Journey id is in proper
format but is not found in the BicycleJourney database.
BicycleJourneyRepository
A Bicycle Journey Repository interface that extends CrudRepository.
CityBicycleJourneys
The main class for the City Bicycle Journeys App.

For importing City Bicycle Stations and Bicycle Journeys into the H2
database as well as for showing commands for opening the app in the
browser and commands for REST requests.

Implements the CommandLineRunner interface.
CitybicyclejourneysApplicationTests
 
ExceptionInfo
A class for Exception information to be shown in a Response Entity.
IdNotANumberException
A class for returning the id that is not in a number format.
ResponseEntityExceptionHandler
A class for giving advice regarding Response Entity Exceptions within
Controller classes.
Station
A Station class, that is used when Station objects are added to the
Station database and for getting Station related data.
StationController
A Station Controller class used to make accessing City Bicycle Station
related data possible with the help of endpoints and other methods.
StationNotFoundException
This class is for Exceptions where a Station id is in proper format
but the Station is not found in the Station database.
StationRepository
A Station repository interface which extends CrudRepository.
The Repository types are Station and Integer.
